Contact Our Event Team
FAQs
Can we book your location for private events?
Of course!  Our brewery is the perfect place to plan your surprise party, company meeting or wedding or rehearsal dinner. We have hundreds of ways to accommodate your event.
Please contact
info@walkingtreebrewery.com
for booking info.
Contact Our Event Team
Learn more about our Event Spaces
Do you serve food?
We do not have a restaurant but we have an excellent food truck on site and we do have some great bar snacks available.  You can always bring take-out or grandma’s lasagna!
Are you family friendly?
Yes, kids are welcome until 8pm.  Please keep them with you and kindly leave the toys at home.
Can I bring my dog or my alpaca?
﻿
We miss our pups around here. Unfortunately the city health code does not allow us to have pets, even your alpaca.
Can I purchase a keg?
Absolutely, call the tasting room during business hours and reserve one today!
What does Stay Rooted mean?
﻿
The mangrove tree is what holds our estuaries in place, they change the water, they build the shorelines. They give community a place to thrive. Our goal is to be like the mangrove, in practice, promise and our people. That’s you.
How long before my order ships?
We ship orders from the shop on Mondays and Fridays. You’ll get a shipment notification with a tracking number when your order ships.
